<p>bivouac &amp; Johnson saved the situation by discovering a limestone cave into which we moved &amp; as we had to cook our meals in the same cave we were nearly smoked out for the time being but better the smoke that a wet shirt so we thought.</p>
<p>Jan 2nd 1918</p>
